public class FileDownloaderService
extends FileDownloaderWidget

Service that serves content (allows downloading) of specified files. It is a suicidal service that kills itself after having served file content once.

Author:
Taimo Peelo (taimo@araneaframework.org), Alar Kvell (alar@araneaframework.org)
